    "Background": {
      "text": "Goodpasture syndrome (60%):\ndiffuse alveolar hemorrhage\n+ acute\nglomerulonephritis\nGoodpasture disease:\nglomerulonephritis\nalone (30%,) pulmonary symptoms alone (10%,)\nAnti-GBM disease is most precise term for both entities\nType II hypersensitivity causing linear IG deposition in glomerular and alveolar BM\nTriggered by:\nSepsis\nURI\nInhalation injury\nSmoking\nPulmonary edema",
