    "Clinical_Features": {
      "text": "Constitutional symptoms prior to pulmonary/renal complications\nPulmonary\nCough\n,\ndyspnea\n,\nchest pain\n,\nhemoptysis\n,\nrespiratory failure\nor\npulmonary hemorrhage\nRenal:\nglomerulonephritis\nHematuria\n,\nproteinuria\n, RBC casts\nSymptoms are often rapidly progressive",
