    "Evaluation": {
      "text": "Pulmonary\nDepends whether patient stable or not, massive\nhemoptysis\nor not\nConsider:\nCXR\nvs CT chest w/contrast, CBC, coags, T&S, bronchoscopy\nRenal:\nUrinalysis\n, CBC, Chemistry, Albumin (often reduced in acute glomerulonephritis,) C3, C4, ASO, ANCA",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
